dc_title_s: Counties and Minor Civil Divisions (Cities and Townships), 1990: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This is a polygon layer of county and minor civil divisions (cities and townships)  in the 7-county Twin Cities metropolitan area as of 1990.  NOTES: - Lines are of limited positional accuracy - COMCDLUT (or comcdlut.dbf) is an available table with additional county/mcd attributes.  However, it is geared toward more recent data. - Some MCDs are split between two counties.  Only those parts of MCDs within the 7-county area are included.
